  "3247200": {
    "name": "Dawn of Ages",
    "steam_appid": 3247200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验真实的中古战争，掠夺武器，率领你的军队出征！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在中古时代初期，建造你的城堡，运用历史上真实的武器和盔甲发展你的军队。沿着历史的足迹，向敌对文明进军。挑战你的对手，在战场上摧毁他们的帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/3e56cadaa4ead84331d9e7cbfb6c0f16.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/3e56cadaa4ead84331d9e7cbfb6c0f16.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🗡️没有龙，没有魔法，现在没有，将来也没有。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dawn of Ages》是一款基于历史准确性的游戏。游戏中没有奇幻生物，没有神秘法术，只有真实的古代帝国和前所未有的策略战争。你所使用的每一种武器、盔甲和战术都基于古代战场的现实。这不仅仅是一款普通的城堡游戏——这是你重温真实历史的机会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/62f7ba5d2239ab63f34d5ed9ee05001b.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/62f7ba5d2239ab63f34d5ed9ee05001b.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚔️史诗级战争等待着你！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥你的部队，参与残酷的大规模战争。制定和执行策略，这些策略与真实的历史冲突如出一辙。用历史上的盔甲和武器定制你的军队，并在策略游戏中运用你的策略，这将考验你的战术能力的极限。胜利取决于你是否能够在战场上胜过你的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/025a6ecd7723f766e489735dd29d8e73.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/025a6ecd7723f766e489735dd29d8e73.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏰建造和扩张你的文明！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Dawn of Ages》中不断进步，你需要管理和扩张你的帝国。建造强大的城堡，招募工人，将你简陋的村庄变成繁荣的中世纪城市。你建造的每一座建筑都会直接影响你发动战争、训练士兵和收集资源的能力。无论你是在寻找下一个伟大的文明游戏，还是一个考验你建筑技能的城堡游戏，《Dawn of Ages》都能满足你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/1c0c7f48fba8490d0754e0638c11ae68.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/1c0c7f48fba8490d0754e0638c11ae68.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🛡️定制你的军队和装备！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Dawn of Ages》中，没有两支相同的军队。你可以从超过100种独特的历史武器、盾牌和盔甲中进行选择，来装备你的部队。每件装备都具有不同的优势，可以扭转战局。战略家们会喜欢这种深度定制，以及为任何情况打造完美军队的可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/308ca446e3b77242e8978c50eacdb5f8.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/308ca446e3b77242e8978c50eacdb5f8.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔥引人入胜的游戏性和简单的操作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验中古战争的刺激，《Dawn of Ages》提供沉浸式、快节奏的战斗和易于使用的界面。无论你是否喜欢策略游戏，或者只是在寻找快速、令人满意的战斗游戏，《Dawn of Ages》都将指挥权掌握在你的手中。建立你的帝国，征服你的敌人，并在史诗般的战略战争游戏中超越竞争对手的文明！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/ba83801b4aa9ceb9d17874d86eaabff8.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/ba83801b4aa9ceb9d17874d86eaabff8.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌐跨平台支持，随时随地畅玩！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dawn of Ages》提供无缝的跨平台游戏体验，让你可以在PC和移动设备上尽情享受游戏。无论是在家还是外出，你都可以访问你的账号，继续你的旅程，不会错过任何精彩内容。与朋友组队，或与其他平台的玩家竞争。随时随地体验在史诗级战争中战斗的自由！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras/af01877cdc1147229e6186d3291d0093.avif?t=1755524835\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247200/extras_big/af01877cdc1147229e6186d3291d0093.avif?t=1755524835 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
